title: Julian Lage on Gary Burton, Nels Cline and his Solo Guitar Project
description: In part two of this interview with Julian Lage during the 2013 Jazz Cruise, the acclaimed guitarist talks about working with Gary Burton and Nels Cline, as well as the influence of Jim Hall. He also discusses his plans for a solo guitar project. Interview by Irene Lee.  Video production by Lee Mergner.
